She jumped and turned around.  She smiled as she saw Skulletron 
standing the. "Hello handsome."

She knew that if they stayed together too long, thier cover might be 
blown.  She smiled and walked towards him, swaying her hips and 
moving her tail gracefully as she walked. "I don't suppose you might 
want to give me a hand looking for some more parts that I might be 
able to use in my lab? Would you?" She siad in a soft, purring voice.
